			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=2646&amp;sid=37752b906c0d5ea37593b492da801015#p2646"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=2646&amp;sid=37752b906c0d5ea37593b492da801015#p2646" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#2</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2&amp;sid=37752b906c0d5ea37593b492da801015" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Jordan Tuwiner</a></strong> &raquo; June 5th, 2011, 10:22 pm <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

